Class ApiCaller

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oddworks.device.request.ApiCaller

  • public class ApiCaller
extends java.lang.Object
    Class of methods for handling api calls. Is instantiated using the ReqeustServicesInitializer and afterward can be accessed through the instance field
